<h3>Specify a Mail Server</h3><p>If you need to specify a mail server to route all emails through then you can enter it in to the box provided.&nbsp; Be sure to select Yes in the &quot;Specify a Mail Server&quot; drop down box or the settings will be ignored.&nbsp; You should only specify a mail server if you need to.&nbsp; If you do not know, you should consult your webhosting provider.




